### Sceanrio 1. Order a Mobile
###

### Step 1 - Order a Mobile
POST http://localhost:5000/api/provisioner
content-type: application/json

{
	"Name" : "Neil Armstrong",
	"ContactPhoneNumber" : "00123456789"
}

### Get the Mobile, so we can get the Order Reference (orderHistory.globalId)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/mobiles/02b3f342-9c08-4c68-8324-4ec88ecc497e

### Step 2 - Mobile Order Completed
POST http://localhost:5001/api/orders/5AD202C5-F96E-43F0-98A0-23FDCC97F222/complete

### Step 3 - Activate a Mobile
POST http://localhost:5000/api/mobiles/20110CA0-AC94-447E-9888-1E048FC2A4C5/activate
content-type: application/json

{
	"Name" : "Neil Armstrong",
	"ContactPhoneNumber" : "00123456789"
}

### Step  4 - Activate Order Completed
POST http://localhost:5002/api/orders/41F139A0-7224-470C-80D1-4DD6291F376A/complete

